arts.ttl: Chelsea lead the race to sign Ajax’s 18-year-old star
arts.sum: According to Caught Offside via VoetbalPrimeur, Chelsea are currently leading the race for Jorrel Hato (18).

arts.ttl: Antony takes Ajax to court for conduct prior to £86m Man Utd move
arts.sum: Antony moved to Manchester United in the summer of 2022 after months of negotiations with former club Ajax.

arts.ttl: Manchester United winger Antony takes former club Ajax to court over 'unlawful' fines ahead of his £85.5m move
arts.sum: Manchester United winger Antony has taken his former club Ajax to court, accusing the Dutch giants of 'unlawfully' fining him ahead of his 2022 move to Old Trafford.
